 <p>
  You progress in Career Mode through four main avenues: Certifications, Specializations, Missions, and Companies.
 </p>
 <!-- No repeatable ad for zone: character count repeatable. -->
 <!-- Repeatable debug data: {"injection":"none","adPosition":2,"startingPoint":0,"skipEvery":null,"nbrPlacementFilledEachSkip":2,"nbrPlacementsScanned":2,"ruleCount":1000,"degradationStartingPoint":1,"stopAds":null,"actualCount":352} -->
 <h3 id="certifications">
  Certifications
 </h3>
 <p>
  There are over 20 certifications in Career Mode, each unlocking specific Specializations. These licenses are required to purchase and pilot different types of aircraft and commercialize your piloting skills. For example, to transport passengers for profit, you need the Charter Service certification.
 </p>
 <!-- No repeatable ad for zone: character count repeatable. -->
 <!-- Repeatable debug data: {"injection":"none","adPosition":2,"startingPoint":0,"skipEvery":null,"nbrPlacementFilledEachSkip":2,"nbrPlacementsScanned":2,"ruleCount":1000,"degradationStartingPoint":1,"stopAds":null,"actualCount":652} -->
 <h3 id="specializations">
  Specializations
 </h3>
 <p>
  Your certifications determine your Specialization. For instance, obtaining the Search &amp; Rescue certification makes it one of your specialties, with corresponding missions appearing on the overworld map.
 </p>
 <!-- No repeatable ad for zone: character count repeatable. -->
 <!-- Repeatable debug data: {"injection":"none","adPosition":2,"startingPoint":0,"skipEvery":null,"nbrPlacementFilledEachSkip":2,"nbrPlacementsScanned":2,"ruleCount":1000,"degradationStartingPoint":1,"stopAds":null,"actualCount":858} -->
 <h3 id="missions">
  Missions
 </h3>
 <p>
  Depending on your Specialization, different missions appear on the overworld map. These vary in objectives, durations, and rewards and are randomly generated across the map. Most missions are time-limited and refreshed periodically.
 </p>
 <!-- Repeatable debug data: {"injection":"before","adPosition":2,"startingPoint":0,"skipEvery":null,"nbrPlacementFilledEachSkip":2,"nbrPlacementsScanned":2,"ruleCount":1000,"degradationStartingPoint":1,"stopAds":null,"isEarlyInjection":false,"actualCount":1090} -->
 <!-- Zone: character count repeatable. -->
 <!-- Repeatable debug data: {"injection":"after","adPosition":3,"startingPoint":0,"skipEvery":null,"nbrPlacementFilledEachSkip":3,"nbrPlacementsScanned":2,"ruleCount":1000,"degradationStartingPoint":1,"stopAds":null,"isEarlyInjection":false,"actualCount":0} -->
 <!-- Repeatable debug data: {"isEarlyInjection":false,"currentRuleCount":1000,"actualCount":0,"hasActualCountMetThreshold":null,"countRemainingForInjection":null,"nextBlockCount":null,"hasCountRemainingForInjectionMetThreshold":null} -->
 <p>
  Missions are divided into
  <strong>
   standard and special
  </strong>
  , with special missions requiring more demanding prerequisites, involving complex aircraft, long transportation tasks, or challenging circumstances. They offer higher payouts and are an excellent way to farm Credits.
 </p>
 <!-- No repeatable ad for zone: character count repeatable. -->
 <!-- Repeatable debug data: {"injection":"none","adPosition":3,"startingPoint":0,"skipEvery":null,"nbrPlacementFilledEachSkip":3,"nbrPlacementsScanned":3,"ruleCount":1000,"degradationStartingPoint":1,"stopAds":null,"actualCount":262} -->
 <h3 id="companies">
  Companies
 </h3>
 <p>
  After earning enough Credits, you can invest in aviation businesses through the Companies tab. These businesses unlock more missions and generate passive income. To keep your company active, you must obtain the necessary licenses, maintain your aircraft, and uphold a good reputation by avoiding incidents and crashes.
 </p>
 <!-- No repeatable ad for zone: character count repeatable. -->
 <!-- Repeatable debug data: {"injection":"none","adPosition":3,"startingPoint":0,"skipEvery":null,"nbrPlacementFilledEachSkip":3,"nbrPlacementsScanned":3,"ruleCount":1000,"degradationStartingPoint":1,"stopAds":null,"actualCount":580} -->
