 <!-- Repeatable debug data: {"isEarlyInjection":false,"currentRuleCount":1000,"actualCount":0,"hasActualCountMetThreshold":null,"countRemainingForInjection":null,"nextBlockCount":null,"hasCountRemainingForInjectionMetThreshold":null} -->
 <!-- No winning ad found for zone: native in content! -->
 <h2 id="donkey-kong-country-returns-hd-makes-a-change-to-the-background">
  Donkey Kong Country Returns HD Makes a Change to the Background
 </h2>
 <!-- No repeatable ad for zone: character count repeatable. -->
 <!-- Repeatable debug data: {"injection":"none","adPosition":2,"startingPoint":0,"skipEvery":null,"nbrPlacementFilledEachSkip":2,"nbrPlacementsScanned":2,"ruleCount":1000,"degradationStartingPoint":1,"stopAds":null,"actualCount":240} -->
 <p>
  Besides pointing out this neat Easter egg, the video seems to be poking fun at the fact that the footage of the Wii and Switch versions of
  <em>
   Donkey Kong Country Returns HD
  </em>
